Platmin Says Employees of Its Mining Contractor Disrupted Mine Operations

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-06-24T11:32:29Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-24/platmin-says-employees-of-its-mining-contractor-disrupted-mine-operations.html
Platmin Ltd. (PPN)  said certain employees
working for one of its mining contractors “illegally disrupted
operations” at its Pilanesburg platinum mine in  South Africa .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
